//   sum(rate(cache_gets_total{result='hit'}[5m]))
//   / sum(rate(cache_gets_total[5m])) * 100
// Alert: < 80% (cold cache or too many evictions)

// Panel 3: Error rate by service
// PromQL:
//   sum by (service) (rate(http_client_requests_seconds_count{outcome='SERVER_ERROR'}[5m]))
//   / sum by (service) (rate(http_client_requests_seconds_count[5m])) * 100
